cs.SD, cs.SY, cs.IT, cs.LG, cs.AI

Reasoning: 
- cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with denoising TDOAs for acoustic source localization.
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also likely as the paper involves pre-processing and improving the accuracy of TDOA measurements, which can be seen as a control problem.
- cs.IT (Information Theory) is another possibility as the paper involves analyzing and processing noisy data.
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possibility as the paper may involve using machine learning techniques for denoising TDOAs.
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also a possibility as the paper may involve using AI techniques for denoising TDOAs.
